<p>The estate was one of 11 estates <a href="https://democracy.walthamforest.gov.uk/documents/s10654/4.2.%20LSP%20report%20-%20Estates%20Review.pdf">identified</a> for possible redevelopment in a 2010 Estates Capacity Study.</p>

