<p>The scheme is being progressed in a joint venture with developer Countryside properties. Phase one of the scheme is approaching completion while the remainder of the estate remains fully occupied.</p>

<p>The redevelopment is being <a href="/approved/funding">funded</a> by the Mayor and has been granted an <a href="/approved/ballotrequirements">exemption</a> from his requirement to ballot residents.</p>
